{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01PbWzEpF8wS5fvYi4MBXtMf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Everything is working. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Root cause**: The ES pods had no monitoring sidecars, and ES was configured to log only to stdout (no log files for Filebeat to read).\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`es-log4j2-config` ConfigMap** — Extended the default `log4j2.properties` to add a `RollingFile` appender alongside the existing `Console` appender. ES now writes `es-cluster_server.json` to the shared logs volume that Filebeat can read.\n\n2. **`es-metricbeat-config` ConfigMap** — Metricbeat configured to use the `elasticsearch` module with `xpack.enabled: true`, connecting to `https://localhost:9200` (using the CA cert from `es-http-tls`), and shipping to the monitoring cluster.\n\n3. **`es-filebeat-config` ConfigMap** — Filebeat configured with the `elasticsearch` module reading `*_server.json` and `gc.log*` from the shared log volume, shipping to the monitoring cluster.\n\n4. **StatefulSet patch** — Added 5 volumes (`es-logs` emptyDir, `log4j2-config`, `metricbeat-config`, `filebeat-config`, `es-ca`) and two new sidecar containers (`metricbeat`, `filebeat`) to every pod.\n\n**Verified results:**\n- All 3 ES pods show `3/3` with containers `elasticsearch`, `metricbeat`, `filebeat`\n- ES cluster health is **green** (3 nodes, 0 unassigned shards)\n- Monitoring cluster now contains:\n  - `.monitoring-es-7-mb-2026.07.03` — 58 docs of xpack stack monitoring metrics (Metricbeat path)\n  - `filebeat-7.17.9-2026.07.03` — 2733 docs of ES logs (Filebeat path)"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1009,"cache_read_input_tokens":84723,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1009},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"20e70b02-dca6-4848-a317-37f37f3d4876","uuid":"315a1076-9cd0-4145-aded-9a2fe2ff196b","request_id":"req_011Ccfku5YuPoymdroRDZUo4"}
